<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>About | CareerTrack</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/responsive.css" />
</head>
<body>

<%- include("./partials/public-navbar") %>

<main>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <p class="tagline">About CareerTrack</p>
    <h1>Helping Students and Job Seekers Manage Their Career Journey</h1>
    <p>
      CareerTrack is a full-stack job and internship application tracking platform
      designed to help users organize applications, monitor interview progress,
      manage reminders and make smarter career decisions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid">

    <div class="about-content-card">
      <h2>Why CareerTrack?</h2>
      <p>
        Many students and freshers apply to multiple companies through LinkedIn,
        Naukri, company websites, referrals and campus placement drives. But after
        applying, they often forget where they applied, what the current status is,
        when the interview is scheduled, or whether they need to follow up.
      </p>
      <p>
        CareerTrack solves this problem by providing a clean dashboard where users
        can add, update, search and manage every job or internship application in
        one place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content-card">
      <h2>Our Goal</h2>
      <p>
        The goal of CareerTrack is to make the job search process more organized,
        professional and stress-free. Instead of maintaining scattered notes or
        screenshots, users can maintain a structured record of their complete
        application journey.
      </p>
      <p>
        It is especially useful for students, freshers, internship seekers and
        beginners who are actively applying for multiple opportunities.
      </p>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="section-title">
      <p>What We Solve</p>
      <h2>From Confusion to Clarity</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📌 Application Tracking</h3>
        <p>
          Store company name, role, location, status, applied date, interview date,
          source and notes in a structured format.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📊 Progress Overview</h3>
        <p>
          View total applications, applied status, interviews, selections and
          rejections through a clean dashboard.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🔎 Search & Filter</h3>
        <p>
          Quickly find applications using company name, role or current application
          status.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📅 Interview Management</h3>
        <p>
          Save interview dates and upcoming interview information so users do not
          miss important opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🔐 Secure User Account</h3>
        <p>
          The full-stack version includes authentication so each user can manage
          their own private application records.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📩 Reminder Ready</h3>
        <p>
          Email notification and reminder support can be integrated to alert users
          about interviews and follow-ups.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tech-section">
    <div class="section-title">
      <p>Technology</p>
      <h2>Built Using Full Stack Web Technologies</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-stack-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Frontend</h3>
        <p>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Backend</h3>
        <p>Node.js, Express.js</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Database</h3>
        <p>MongoDB with Mongoose</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Authentication</h3>
        <p>JWT and bcrypt</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Notifications</h3>
        <p>Nodemailer Email Alerts</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Deployment</h3>
        <p>GitHub, Render, MongoDB Atlas</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-highlight">
    <div>
      <p class="tagline">Project Vision</p>
      <h2>A Practical Career Management Tool</h2>
      <p>
        CareerTrack is not just a basic CRUD project. It represents a real-world
        problem faced by students and freshers. The project includes responsive UI,
        form validation, local storage testing, CRUD-ready pages, dashboard analytics,
        authentication-ready structure and future backend integration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <h3>Core Modules</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>✔ User Registration and Login</li>
        <li>✔ Application Management</li>
        <li>✔ Dashboard Analytics</li>
        <li>✔ Search and Filter System</li>
        <li>✔ Profile Management</li>
        <li>✔ Reminder and Notification Ready</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to Track Your Career Journey?</h2>
    <p>Start managing your job and internship applications with CareerTrack.</p>
    <a href="/register" class="primary-btn">Create Account</a>
  </section>

</main>

<%- include("./partials/footer") %>

<script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>